{"tid":1809811,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"小米攝錄機睇到其他人屋企 Google停止旗下智能家居產品連結小米產品","createTime":"2020-01-03T10:59:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-03T12:20:07.000Z","uid":236171,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"17ecba6fe87d0934f675191e904f5d25ce6d8d7d","tid":1809811,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T10:59:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200103&amp;s=10829392&amp;a=60446513\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200103%26s%3D10829392%26a%3D60446513&d=GDp31xM3xvXFOTrKf8Ol7Hs01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=056b6545\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200103%26s%3D10829392%26a%3D60446513&h=0b6f3d82\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200103&amp;s=10829392&amp;a=60446513</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">小米攝錄機睇到其他人屋企 Google停止旗下智能家居產品連結小米產品</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nReddit用戶發文，指將小米旗下的米家智能攝錄機1080p連接到Google智能家居裝置Nest Hub時，居然看到了攝錄機畫面為其他用戶的家居影像，事主甚至貼出了相關影片。<br />\n<br />\n事件被外國傳媒報道後，Google表示已得悉情況，目前Google已停止Google Assistant和Home連接至小米裝置。<br />\n<br />\nGoogle發言人表示，已得悉有關事件，目前正在聯絡小米解決問題，但就沒有提到是甚麼問題。以下為Google官方英文發言：<br />\n<br />\n「We're aware of the issue and are in contact with Xiaomi to work on a fix. In the meantime, we're disabling Xiaomi integrations on our devices.」<br />\n<br />\n發文的網民指他所用的是米家智能攝錄機1080p，購自隸屬於阿里巴巴集團的網購平台AliExpress。"},{"pid":"dae341daa1e547c4efa191d98e1b0363607cbceb","tid":1809811,"uid":236171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T11:00:30.000Z","msg":"又係你呀屌米<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb0a1c243fd953e42bd35195c7bd29f841ad4bc4","tid":1809811,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T11:01:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccea8afc847fc2bebc5cd9ea47f0677cc477d743","tid":1809811,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T11:17:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7edc875af65f02d5811fe60312f4d5df2974698d","tid":1809811,"uid":140145,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T11:19:51.000Z","msg":"善心打破零回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2fb1a4ba5724c244874996caa440bbe38716dc0","tid":1809811,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T12:20:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}